heapifyUp(tab, i){
    if(i == 0) return;
    int pIdx = (i-1)/2
    if(tab[i]>tab[p]){
        swap(tab, i, p);
        return heapifyUp(tab, p);
    }
    return;
}

heapifyDown(tab, i, n){
    int cIdx = 2*i+1;
    if(n <= 1 || cIdx > n) return;
    if(tab[cIdx]<tab[cIdx+1]){
        cIdx++;
    }
    if(tab[cIdx]>tab[i]){
        swap(tab, i, cIdx);
        heapifyDown(tab, cIdx, n);
    }
    return
}

swap(tab, i1, i2){
    tmp := tab[i2];
    tab[i2] = tab[i1];
    tab[i1] = tmp;

			"text": "4|5)\n\nheapifyUp(tab, i){\n    if(i == 0) return;\n    int pIdx = (i-1)/2\n    if(tab[i]>tab[p]){\n        swap(tab, i, p);\n        return heapifyUp(tab, p);\n    }\n    return;\n}\n\nheapifyDown(tab, i, n){\n    int cIdx = 2*i+1;\n    if(n <= 1 || cIdx > n) return;\n    if(tab[cIdx]<tab[cIdx+1]){\n        cIdx++;\n    }\n    if(tab[cIdx]>tab[i]){\n        swap(tab, i, cIdx);\n        heapifyDown(tab, cIdx, n);\n    }\n    return\n}\n\nswap(tab, i1, i2){\n    tmp := tab[i2];\n    tab[i2] = tab[i1];\n    tab[i1] = tmp;\n    return;\n}",
